OL,5,MElectromagnetic Field 2026: news and
OL,7,Mupdates
OL,9,GElectromagnetic Field is only a few
OL,10,Gmonths away and this is the first of
OL,11,Gseveral updates to help you prepare.
OL,12,GIn this blog post (which we’re also
OL,13,Gsending as emails to the address you
OL,14,Gbought your tickets with), we’ll be
OL,15,Gupdating you on things to do at EMF,
OL,16,Gand helping you with what to bring in
OL,17,Gorder to have a great time. Closer to
OL,18,Gthe date, we’ll also send summaries of
OL,19,Gconditions on the field, so that you
OL,20,Gknow whether to pack warm or pack
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
